<!-- crosswire:start -->
## Inter-Instance Communication

This project uses `crosswire` for cross-instance coordination.
- Your identity and peers are in `xw.json`
- Always use the `./xw` CLI for all operations. Never construct raw shell commands for messaging.
- Check inbox: `./xw check` -- do this when starting a task
- Read a message: `./xw read <id>`
- Send a message: `./xw send [--to <name>] <type> [--re <id>] "body"`
- Mark done: `./xw done <id>`
- List peers: `./xw peers`
- Sync peer list: `./xw sync`
<!-- crosswire:end -->
